OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine and warm day with plenty
OL,6,Fof sunshine, though it will be rather
OL,7,Fbreezy in the north. Sunshine may turn
OL,8,Fhazy in places during the afternoon,
OL,9,Fbut will remain strong enough to give
OL,10,Fhigh UV levels.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FWinds will gradually ease
OL,13,Fthrough the evening, leading to a dry
OL,14,Fnight with largely clear skies. A
OL,15,Fchance of mist and shallow fog in
OL,16,Fprone areas around dawn.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FGenerally fine and dry with
OL,19,Flight winds. Bright though staying
OL,20,Frather cloudy through the day. Feeling
OL,21,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
